data.text:
Xpansion Enterprise, Inc., a Foreign Profit Corporation, is a business entity located in Boca Raton, FL. Officially filed on April 26, 2021, this corporation is recognized under the document number F21000002674. Governed by the Florida Department Of State, the corporation is in Inactive filing status, and entity's FEI/EIN number is 85-3317650.

The principal address of the corporation is located at 621 Nw 53rd Street Ste240, Boca Raton, FL 33487 and mailing address is at 501 E Las Olas Blvd Ste 300, Ft Lauderdale, FL 33301, serving as the central hub for its business operations and correspondence.

The corporation is led by a team of key individuals: Azuara, Monik from Ft Lauderdale FL, holding the position of DPA.

Ensuring the legal and official compliance of the corporation, Azuara, Monika acts as the registered agent. He is based at the same address as the corporation's principal address. As of the last update, this corporation had not filed any annual reports, reflecting its recent inception into the business world.
